go_town.description:
You stand in a big, but dirty, square. Almost all houses in the town are old and dirty. Only four look worth noticing:

- a one-story building with a bright sign "Crimson Plate Restaurant";

- a three-story brick building with the words "Velvet Nights Hotel";

- a plastic building with a red cross on the door and windows (looks like a small clinic);

- a white two-story house with a four-color flag on the roof.

A wide road goes away from the square. It leads to a small factory with two chimneys, sending out black smoke. You might be able to reach the checkpoint using this road.
